descriptionNullable:
How do two philosophically contrasting concepts play out in the world of data?
I decided to glean some insights from global data by analyzing suicide rates and happiness scores from the WHO and World Happiness Report projects respectively for the period of 2015-2019.
I found some interesting stuff. See the dataset and my published notebook(portefeuille). Enjoy.😊
